---
description: Do not add code comments unless explicitly requested
alwaysApply: true
---

# No Comments

- Do not add comments to code you write or edit.
- Do not add JSDoc, TODO comments, or explanatory inline comments.
- Prefer clear naming and structure over comments.
- Only add a comment if the user explicitly asks for one, or if it is required to satisfy a linter/tooling rule already present in the file.
